description: This workout is meant for beginners wanting to build strength. It focuses on heavy compount movements with low rep numbers and low sets. Because of the intensity of this workout, recommended rest times are from 60 to 90 seconds between each set.

This workout is meant for advanced users wanting to build strength. This workout focuses on heavy compound movements. The sets and rep ranges assigned to each exercise is to be lifted at 85% to 95% of your one rep max of that exercise. These are the working sets of each exercise. It is up to you to decide how much warm up sets to do before you hit your working sets. Rest times between each set should be 1-2 minutes
